# Google Photos Shared Album — for guest photo/video uploads
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com and create a project
# 2. Enable the Photos Library API
# 3. Create an API key (restrict to Photos Library API)
# 4. Create a shared album in Google Photos and copy its album ID
#    (the album ID is in the URL when you open the album: albums/ALBUM_ID)
# 5. For batchCreate (media item creation), an API key alone won't work —
#    you'll need OAuth 2.0 credentials. See:
#    https://developers.google.com/photos/library/guides/get-started
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_PHOTOS_ALBUM_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_PHOTOS_API_KEY=
